data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the picturesque Chouteau Hills neighborhood! This stunning property offers an abundance of space with 5 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, a large living room, a sunroom that can double as an extra living or dining room, and not one but two huge master bedrooms. Situated on a generous 1.25-acre lot, this home provides room to roam and create lasting memories with your loved ones. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to own a piece of Chouteau Hills paradise. Whether you're looking for space, comfort, or room to grow, this home has it all. The seller is offering a generous 1-year home warranty for your peace of mind and $ 3,500 in paint/carpet allowances, giving you the flexibility to make personalized updates.
